Taal -LRB- English : Rhythm -RRB- is a 1999 Bollywood musical romantic drama film co written , edited , produced and directed by Subhash Ghai .
Taal was an official selection for the 2005 Ebertfest : Roger Ebert 's Film Festival .
Taal was screened retrospectively , during the 2014 International Film Festival of India in the Celebrating Dance in Indian cinema section .
The film stars Anil Kapoor , Akshaye Khanna , Aishwarya Rai , Amrish Puri and Alok Nath .
It was also dubbed in Tamil as Thaalam .
It was very successful in India and overseas , becoming the first Indian film to reach the top 20 on Variety 's box office list .
Anil Kapoor , A. R. Rahman , Alka Yagnik and Anand Bakshi each won a Filmfare Award for their work in the film .